# Mark third-party skill content as vendored + generated so GitHub:
#   - excludes it from language statistics
#   - collapses diffs by default in PR views
# Skills are managed by `npx skills` (vercel-labs/skills) and refreshed via
# `./scripts/setup.sh update-skills`. Local skills authored in this repo are
# the same shape as upstream ones; treat them the same to keep the rule simple.
skills/** linguist-vendored=true
skills/** linguist-generated=true
